  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The treatment of ADHD in jail will help the prisoners in their rehabilitation process
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
  <detailed_description>
    <textblock>
      Prisoners with ADHD will be offered treatment with Stratera, and we wanted to study their use
      of the prisons rehabilitation offers as school, programs and work training before and after
      treatment with Stratera.
    </textblock>
  </detailed_description>
